Use varargs variants of libsparqlclient query mechanisms throughout.

Class and property derivation should be described in RDF, and understand
subclasses/subproperties.

Sifting/splitting on de-assertion.

Apply same-origin policies to assertions to reduce potential for pollution.

White-listing and black-listing.

When a proxy is created or updated, proxies for entities referencing the
entities it's a proxy for should also be updated so that new in-bound
references can be properly proxied.

The proxy graph behaviour should be configurable -- i.e., whether to write
all proxies into a single graph, or a graph-per-proxy.
